157
00:10:49,383 --> 00:10:50,216
Kiera!

158
00:10:50,217 --> 00:10:50,916
Sam!

159
00:10:50,917 --> 00:10:51,583
Sam!

160
00:10:51,584 --> 00:10:52,183
